For the regular Caesar shift, the method iterates through each character in the string and shifts it by the normalized shift value. Only alphabetic characters are shifted, while non-alphabetic characters are left unchanged. The method uses the `StringBuilder` class to efficiently build the resulting string, and returns the final result as a string.

